"Show JSON tokens themselves instead of token names ``T_*`` in the JSON "
"decoder error messages (:tarantool-issue:`4339`)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Show a decoding context in the JSON decoder error messages (:tarantool-"
"issue:`4339`)."
msgstr ""

