msgstr ""

msgid "Replication"
msgstr "Репликация"

msgid ""
"It is now possible to specify synchro quorum as a function of a number ``N``"
" of registered replicas instead of a ``const`` number, for example:"
msgstr ""

msgid "box.cfg{replication_synchro_quorum = \"N/2 + 1\"}"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Only the non-anonymous bootstrapped replicas amount to ``N``. The expression"
" should respect synchro guarantees: at least 50% of the cluster size + 1. "
"The expression value is re-evaluated automatically inside of Tarantool when "
"new replicas appear or old ones are removed (:tarantool-issue:`5446`)."
msgstr ""

